'''Julie Eccles''' is an actress who provided the voice of [[Jan Ors]] in ''[[Star Wars: Dark Forces]]'' and played [[Ru Murleen]] in the live-action cutscenes of ''[[Star Wars: Rebel Assault II: The Hidden Empire]]''. Years earlier, she had a minor role in [[Wikipedia:Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade|''Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade'']] as [[Indiana Jones]]'s secretary, [[Wikia:c:Indianajones:Irene|Irene]].

